%description:
Verify that if a folder listed in ".nedfolders" doesn't exist, it causes an error.

%file: .oppfeatures
<features/>

%file: .nedfolders
src
bogus

%file: testscript.sh
mkdir -p src
opp_featuretool list

%testprog: sh ./testscript.sh

%exitcode: 1

%contains: stderr
opp_featuretool: Consistency check failed: NED source folder 'bogus' listed in '.nedfolders' does not exist

